<p>Group get together out on the slopes - Making time to spend with your friends couldn't be done in a better way than out on the slopes, cosy drinks around the fire, or fine-dining with views of the mountains. Inghams offer fantastic group skiing and snowboarding holidays to suit any size.</p>
<p>We’ll help you arrange your group holiday, so you can simply enjoy being with your friends. You’ll get a personal groups advisor who can help organise the individual needs of any group. Plus we’ve got lots of offers to ensure the best group ski holiday.</p>
<h2>Group skiing holiday offers</h2>
<p>We offer some great group holiday options for skiing and snowboarding, here are some highlights when booking with Inghams:</p>
