<p>Based on the above resorts, here are some accommodation options for those destinations that are ideal for group booking, whether you are looking for a <a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets">catered chalet</a>, a <a data-udi="umb://document/31c3c6181bb642ffab4ba3d3f4762c55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/31c3c6181bb642ffab4ba3d3f4762c55}" title="Hotels">hotel with half-board</a> options or even <a data-udi="umb://document/97cadeaefe8d4029aa226520f176e71f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/97cadeaefe8d4029aa226520f176e71f}" title="Self Catering Apartments">self catered apartments</a>:</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
