<p><img src="/media/13102560/601-a.jpg" alt="LeSavoie" data-udi="umb://media/70a786bff7f54f65abb32afb93eb53a5" /></p>
<p>The hotel is in central Val d'Isere and just a short walk from the Solaise Express Lift. You can opt for half-board catering and enjoy the wellness area.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b741a67aaee94a26bd6d0e0112846efc}" title="Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie" class="c-btn">Hotel Le Savoie</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/da86002e01f540c788f2ac845c8099a5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da86002e01f540c788f2ac845c8099a5}" title="Village Montana Apartments">Village Montana Apartments</a></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13105474/village-montana-527x251.jpg" alt="VillageMontana" data-udi="umb://media/6031ba569326486292afe6a611aaf781" /></p>
<p>These self-catering (or half-board) apartments are based on a sunny slope side location. Equipped with all you need and use of the hotel spa.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/da86002e01f540c788f2ac845c8099a5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da86002e01f540c788f2ac845c8099a5}" title="Village Montana Apartments" class="c-btn">View Apartments</a></p>
